tool_description: Get the basic metadata on all breeds of dogs from around the world. Check out encurate.app to manage content on your mobile apps. Contact to feature your app on encurate.app website.
name: DogBreedDB
title: DogBreedDB

api_list.name: Paginated
api_list.description: Get all dog breed results in a set of 10 per page.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://dogbreeddb.p.rapidapi.com/paginated/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "dogbreeddb.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
